@startuml AgenticArchitect_Corrected_Workflow
!theme plain
skinparam ConditionEndStyle hline

title Logical Flow: AgenticArchitect (English Version)

|User|
start
:Submit Requirements (PDF/Docx);

|#F9F9F9|Project Manager Agent|
repeat
  :Analyze Project Charter;
  note right
    **Validation Checklist:**
    - Project Name & Description
    - Context Definition
    - SMART Objectives
    - Scope, Limits & Risks
    - Assumptions (I/O, Resources)
    - Expected Deliverables
  end note
  
  if (Is Charter SMART & Complete?) then (No)
    :Generate Clarification Questionnaire;
    |User|
    :Provide Missing Details;
    |#F9F9F9|Project Manager Agent|
  else (Yes)
    :Generate Validated Project Charter;
    break
  endif
repeat while (Still missing info?) is (Yes)

|#E3F2FD|Architect Agent|
:Requirement Analysis (Bull's Eye / Octopus);
:Maturity Study (SOTA / TRL Assessment);
:Design Architecture Diagrams (BPMN, SADT);
:Define Solution Type (POC/MVP/App);
:Define Stakeholders (RACI) & Planning;
:Define User Stories (Spec -> Test -> Code);
:Generate Technical Architecture Dossier (TAD);

|#F1F8E9|Developer Agent (IA/Data/Devops)|
:Initialize CI/CD & Containers;
:Build Functional Skeleton (V-Cycle);

partition "Iterative Agile / SOLID Loop" {
  repeat
    :Define Functional Unit;
    :Manage Data Pipeline;
    :Write Unit Tests;
    :Implement SOLID Functionality;
    if (Tests Passed?) then (No)
      :Auto-debug & Refactor;
    else (Yes)
      :Commit & Integrate;
      break
    endif
  repeat while (Bug detected?) is (Yes)
}

|User|
:Receive Final Solution (Code, Docs, Slides);
stop

@enduml